             was indicted for <rs id="t18290409-280-off1578" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290409-280-off1578" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290409-280-off1578" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290409-280-cd1579" type="crimeDate">26th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290409-280-off1578 t18290409-280-cd1579"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290409-280-off1580 t18290409-280-cd1579"></join>. 3 jugs, value 2s. 6d.; 12 pap boats, value 3s.; 4 busts, value 5s.; 65 egg-cups, value 1ls.; 58 cups, value 6s. 6d.; 54 saucers, value 5s. 6d.; 29 basons, value 7s.: 1 milk-pot, value 3d.; 7 glass cruets, value 14s.; 144 toys, value 2s.; 148 plates, value 18s. 6d.; 54 saltcellars, value 8s.; 12 coffee-cups, value 3s. 6d., and 1 china dog, value 2s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18290409-280-victim2548" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Mansfield
                        <interp inst="t18290409-280-victim2548" type="surname" value="Mansfield"></interp>
